    "[中图分类号]G270.9 Abstract: Confucius isa great practitioner of sorting historical materials and compilating archives and documents.His masterpiece the shang shu is the essence of Chinese traditional culture which reflects his ideology on the compilation of archives and documents in many ways such asputing a new premium on archives and documents,seting a high value on their compilating，having clear goals in mind,holding objectiveatitude,sorting historical materialspreciselyand appropriately，laying out materialsin a scientific way. Confucius' thoughts have carved out the science of archives and layed a foundation.So nowadays in the daily work of archives，we can learn and draw lessons from Confucius‘ideology on the compilation of archives and documents. Keywords: Shang shu ;Confucius ;Archives and documents ;Compilation ideas 庄子在《庄子·天运》篇中写道：“孔子谓老聃曰：‘丘治《诗》《书》《礼》《乐》《易》《春秋》六经,自以为久矣，孰知其故矣。\"庄子所写很难说是孔子的原话，因为后世研究者认为《易》(即《周易》)和《礼》即《礼记》)并非出自孔子一人之手，而系战国或秦之际儒家的作品，不过《书》即《尚书》被公认为系孔子所编。《诗》即《诗经》)、《春秋》和《尚书》...": "False",
